title: Tesla (NASDAQ: $TSLA) is Cardiff's most Googled stock
Microsoft Forges Long-Term Deal With Boosteroid After Nintendo, Nvidia To Dispel Concerns Over Activision Deal
description: On Tuesday, Microsoft Corp (NASDAQ: MSFT) inked a 10-year deal with Boosteroid to bring Xbox PC games to Boosteroid's cloud gaming platform. Boosteroid, which has its software development team in Ukraine, recently surpassed 4 million users globally. The deal will also enable Boosteroid customers to stream Activision Blizzard, Inc (NASDAQ: ATVI) PC titles after Microsoft acquires the American video gaming company.
